    "testimonial_marquee_9W4yJt": {
      "type": "testimonial-marquee",
      "blocks": {
        "image_8UAFQR": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "icon_select": "100",
            "heading": "My skin has never looked this good",
            "text": "<p>I've tried countless serums and nothing came close. After two weeks my skin is visibly plumper, the texture is smoother and my partner actually noticed the difference. This is my forever product.</p>",
            "author": "<em>- Sophie M., verified customer</em>",
            "icon_image_height_desk": 50,
            "icon_image_height": 40
          }
        },
        "image_ENFMWA": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "icon_select": "100",
            "heading": "Finally a cream that doesn't break me out",
            "text": "<p>As someone with reactive, sensitive skin I was so skeptical. But this cream is genuinely different - it absorbs instantly, doesn't clog my pores and my skin feels balanced all day. I repurchased three times already.</p>",
            "author": "- <em>Isabella K., verified customer</em>",
            "icon_image_height_desk": 50,
            "icon_image_height": 40
          }
        },
        "image_ercjzL": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "icon_select": "100",
            "heading": "Obsessed doesn't even cover it",
            "text": "<p>I use this body scrub every shower and my skin is softer than it's ever been. The scent is incredible and it doesn't leave that greasy film other scrubs do. My friends keep asking what I'm using.</p>",
            "author": "- <em>Zoe R., verified customer</em>",
            "icon_image_height_desk": 50,
            "icon_image_height": 40
          }
        },
        "image_J444Rp": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "icon_select": "100",
            "heading": "Dry skin? What dry skin?",
            "text": "<p>I've struggled with dry patches on my legs and arms for years. This balm sorted it within days - not weeks. I apply it after my shower and my skin stays hydrated until the next morning. Absolutely worth every penny.</p>",
            "author": "- <em>Amelia T., verified customer</em>",
            "icon_image_height_desk": 50,
            "icon_image_height": 40
          }
        },
        "image_BXFPnH": {
          "type": "image",
          "settings": {
            "icon_select": "100",
            "heading": "The glow-up I didn't expect",
            "text": "<p>I bought the serum and cream together and honestly I wasn't expecting much. Three weeks later my skin is glowing, my dark spots have faded and I've stopped wearing foundation to work. People keep telling me I look well-rested. I tell them it's the skincare.</p>",
            "author": "- <em>Charlotte W., verified customer</em>",
            "icon_image_height_desk": 50,
            "icon_image_height": 40
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "image_8UAFQR",
        "image_ENFMWA",
        "image_ercjzL",
        "image_J444Rp",
        "image_BXFPnH"
      ],
